# web-development-fund

web-development-fund is a modern full-stack web application designed to support developers, open-source contributors, startups, and technology communities by providing a centralized platform for funding and collaboration. The platform enables users to create developer profiles, showcase projects, request funding, manage donations, and connect with sponsors or contributors in a secure and transparent environment.

## Features

- User authentication and authorization
- Developer profile management
- Project showcase and submissions
- Funding and donation system
- Sponsor and contributor support
- Secure payment integration
- Real-time progress tracking
- Responsive dashboard interface
- Community collaboration tools
- REST API and database integration

## Technologies

This project can be built using:

- React.js / Next.js
- Node.js and Express.js
- MongoDB or PostgreSQL
- Tailwind CSS
- JWT Authentication
- REST API or GraphQL

## Goals

The main goal of this platform is to create a transparent and scalable ecosystem where developers and organizations can collaborate, support innovation, and fund impactful software projects.

